assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: FinTech Global Incorporated provides various financial services in Japan. It operates through three segments, Investment Banking, Public Management Consulting, and Entertainment service business. The company offers financial arrangements; financial advisory; asset management, including real estate investment and investment fund management; private equity investment; asset investment, aircraft asset management, aircraft technology advisory, and aircraft registry services. It also provides hedge fund management, and investment in renewable energy power generation projects, as well as technical consulting services. In addition, the company owns, operates, manages, and develops a theme park and distributes animated TV- series. FinTech Global Incorporated was incorporated in 1994 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan.
